data.description: Discover the charm of this inviting move-in ready split-level home featuring 3 bedrooms and 2 updated bathrooms.  Experience year-round comfort with the added luxury of mini-split air conditioning & heating in most rooms! Step into relaxation with a nice rear deck, perfect for outdoor enjoyment. The fenced-in back yard offers both privacy & security. Additionally, the basement is a blank canvas, ready for your personal touch to transform it into a functional and inviting space. With the added convenience of a paved driveway, this  home is the perfect blend of comfort and functionality! Call today for your private showing!
